reviewText: James Dunn was good.  The only good thing about this movie.  Sheila Ryan was beautiful.  But she was only in this this movie 3-5 minutes tops.  Why is she said to be the star, when she was barely in the movie?  And it was so short.  I should've read the description more thoroughly.

I always liked James Dunn acting, and in this movie he delivers.
Good story and good acting by all of the cast.
If you like a good mystery, I think you will like this movie.
